This study aimed to evaluate a polyphenol extract from olive oil by-product, to 
improve the preservation of "Fior di latte" cheese during storage. Nine batches 
of "Fior di latte" cheese were manufactured in a local dairy production plant: 
three batches treated with 250 μg/mL of phenols from olive oil by-products in 
